'''Klaipėda city passenger transport''' ({{lang-lt|Klaipėdos keleivinis transportas}}) is a Public Enterprise and public transport service organizing, supervising and coordinating body in [[Klaipėda]] city, [[Lithuania]].
==History== Public Enterprise Klaipėda city passenger transport - was founded on March 27, 2003 by Klaipeda City Municipality Council Decision number 1-81.<ref>{{cite web|author=Software (C) UAB IDAMAS (www.idamas.net) |url=http://www.klaipedatransport.lt/index.php?-452310126 |title=Klaipėdos keleivinis transportas - Apie mus |publisher=Klaipedatransport.lt |date=2009-11-26 |accessdate=2012-11-17}}</ref> Klaipėda city passenger transport administration was granted an office located at Kalnupės g. 1, Klaipėda <ref>{{cite web |author=Klaipėdos keleivinis transportas |url=http://www.klaipedatransport.lt/index.php?410964712 |title=Klaipėdos keleivinis transportas - 2008 metų veiklos ataskaita |accessdate=2012-11-23}}</ref> Klaipeda was the first among the major Lithuanian cities, which declined to obsolete outdated Hungarian Ikarus passenger busses.<ref>{{cite web|author=Solmetra (www.solmetra.com) |url=http://www.linava.lt/cms/content.aspx?root_id=lt&path=/lt/lt_info/lt_info_1&item_id=lt_info_1_19 |title=Linava |publisher=Linava.lt |date= |accessdate=2012-11-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110606161012/http://www.linava.lt/cms/content.aspx?root_id=lt&path=%2Flt%2Flt_info%2Flt_info_1&item_id=lt_info_1_19 |archivedate=2011-06-06 |df= }}</ref> Klaipeda was a first city in Lithuania, which introduced [[electronic ticket]]ing system in Lithianian public transport.<ref>{{cite web|author=|url=http://klaipeda.diena.lt/naujienos/miestas/popieriniu-autobusu-bilietu-neliks-ir-klaipedoje-443445 |title=Popierinių autobusų bilietų neliks ir Klaipėdoje - Klaipėda - Klaipėda |publisher=Klaipeda.diena.lt |date=2012-08-18 |accessdate=2012-11-17}}</ref> In December 2009 Klaipėda city passenger transport headquarters moved from the old office at Kalnupės street 1 to the office at S. Daukanto street 15.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ve.lt/naujienos/lietuva/lietuvos-naujienos/pigesni-autobusu-bilietai---miesto-centre/ |title=Pigesni autobusų bilietai - miesto centre |publisher=ve.lt |date=2010-05-02 |accessdate=2012-11-17}}</ref>
==International projects== Klaipėda city passenger transport is involved in the following international projects: * [[MoCuBa]], * [[PROCEED]], * [[PIMMS Transfer]].,<ref>http://www.klaipedatransport.lt/index.php?2072672061 Všį „Klaipėdos keleivinis transportas" tinklalapis skyrius: "Dalyvavimas tarptautiniuose projektuose". Retrieved: 2012-11-16 22:43 (Lithuanian language)</ref> * [[BAY in TRAP]].<ref>http://bayintrap.eu/wpress/?page_id=74 Bayintrap EU project. Retrieved: 2014-03-11 18:08</ref>
