'''Peter Liechti''' (January 8, 1951 &ndash; 4 April 2014) was a [[Switzerland|Swiss]] movie director. He was born in [[St. Gallen]], Switzerland.
He directed over 100 Swiss-[[German language|German]] movies. He was nominated for many awards. Most of his movies were shown at the [[Berlin International Film Festival]] (BIFF). He was awarded an honorary awards at the BIFF in 2013.
Liechti died on 4 April 2014, aged 63.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nzz.ch/aktuell/feuilleton/film/konfrontationen-mit-dem-innern-daemon-1.18278717|title=Konfrontationen mit dem innern Dämon|publisher=nzz.ch|accessdate=12 April 2014|date=7 April 2014}}</ref>
