[[File:Raees-Logo.jpg|thumb|Raees Coffee New Logo]]
'''Raees Coffee''' is an Iranian [[List of coffeehouse chains|coffeehouse chain]] based in [[Tehran]].<ref name="Schlossberg 2015"/><ref name="Amiri 2011"/> The company was founded in 2000, and currently has seven branches in Tehran. The coffee chain is designed in a manner that emulates Starbucks coffee houses, and included a company logo that was similar to that of Starbucks. In 2016 they changed the logo.<ref name="Schlossberg 2015"/><ref name="Amiri 2011"/><ref name="Khosravi 2011"/>
==See also== * [[List of coffeehouse chains]]
